added.title: Breakfast
added.description: The Titans discover the joys of eating breakfast food for every meal, but will that lead to an old friend becoming too powerful?

added.title: Captain Cool
added.description: The Titans' antics with their imaginary friend Captain Cool annoy Robin until make-believe starts becoming real.

added.title: A Doom Patrol Thanksgiving
added.description: Beast Boy returns home for Thanksgiving and the Doom Patrol enter a float in the town's parade. / The Doom Patrol finds old home movies about themselves that The Chief had hidden.

added.title: Glunkakakakah
added.description: Robin teaches the other Titans the art of concealment through a game of hide and seek.

added.title: Trousering Inferno
added.description: The Bad Guy Busters must reunite to save Izzy after Harold uncovers her previous identity and leads a super villain from her past right to her.

added.title: The Big Bangs Theory
added.description: Chef forgets the password for his computer but knows it has something to do with one of the 99 previous explosions that took out the school. Entering the wrong password will cause the school to blow up for the 100th time.

added.title: Gwen Scary, Gwen Lost
added.description: When Chef discovers his spooky Halloween pranks have never scared the kids he's devastated. Determined to get them this year, he agrees to hand over full control of his pranking to Gwen. Her plan turns out far spookier then Chef ever hoped.

added.title: Mad Math: Taffy Road
added.description: After Courtney refuses to share her taffy winnings from a calculus for candy competition, she's transported to the desolate future where she learns that greed is not without consequence.

added.title: PuzzleMaster
added.description: Victor, Valentino, Charlene and Pineapple awaken to find themselves in a bizarre and scary series of puzzle rooms where the rules are simple: escape or cease to exist!

added.title: Finding Posada
added.description: When Victor and Valentino attempt to win the grand prize of best ofrenda at the Dia de Muertos festival, they enlist the help of legendary artist Jose Guadalupe Posada himself!

added.title: La Catrina
added.description: Valentino is elated to get an exclusive invite to a performance by the famous singer La Catrina in the Underworld. There is just one problem: the invite is for grown-ups only.

added.title: Bone Bike
added.description: Victor and Valentino must tame a wild, living motorcycle made of bones, to win Mic and Hun's Underworld grand-prix: The Muerto Race!

added.title: For Queen and Country
added.description: Onion has an unexpected and impossible new love interest. Off to England then.

added.title: Petri
added.description: Apple and Onion must get back to their apartment to put the lid back on a dangerous petri dish.

added.title: Mandora Saves Christmas
added.description: Santa Claus is on the run from Mandora! Can the Thundercats help him get off Third Earth without getting caught? And can Santa Claus teach them a little something about this weird new holiday "Christmas"?

added.title: #TheAquamanCometh
added.description: For months, Garth's been sending Aquaman letters that greatly exaggerate his accomplishments in Metropolis, so when the King of Atlantis comes for a surprise visit, Garth begs the Super Hero Girls to help cover for his little white lies.

added.title: #OneEnchantedEvening
added.description: Zee worries that Zatara is lonely and volunteers to play matchmaker for her dad.  But when her meddlesome match-matching accidentally sets her dad up with an old enemy, Zee must find a way to fix the mess she made!

added.title: #NightmareInGotham
added.description: Babs and Harleen bring the Girls to Gotham City to celebrate Halloween! However, the fun is put on hold when the SuperHero Girls run into Gotham's most notorious SuperVillain.

added.title: #Beeline
added.description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

added.title: #SuperWho?
added.description: Overwhelmed by the amount of Superman coverage in Metropolis, Supergirl decides to get out there and really show the city what she can do. But when Superman inadvertently puts everyone in harm's way, Supergirl has to decide whether to do what's good for the people or what's good for her ego.

added.title: #ShockItToMe
added.description: Leslie Willis, the meanest girl in school, becomes a social media sensation by posting mean-spirited videos on her MetropoVids channel, causing Wonder Woman to question the moral integrity of the people who live in the World of Man.

added.title: Cat Toy of the Future
added.description: Tiggy's attempt to create a new toy for Gweeseek turns the Department of Lost and Found into Cat Central.

added.title: Picky Prangle
added.description: It's Pie Day! And Prangle Penguin is already way behind on his strawberry pie deliveries. Hoping to improve their helpfulness rating, Tig and Seek take on the task of pie-making, even as things quickly take a not-so-sweet turn.

added.title: Exodus Part 1
added.description: Fleeing the destruction of their home planet Thundera, Lion-O and the ThunderCats land on the mysterious, dangerous, all-around awesome world of Third Earth! But their enemies, the Mutants of Plun-Darr have followed them and it turns out Third Earth already has a Mumm-Ra problem, can Lion-O learn the ropes of being a leader in time?

added.title: Exodus Part 2
added.description: Fleeing the destruction of their home planet Thundera, Lion-O and the ThunderCats land on the mysterious, dangerous, all-around awesome world of Third Earth! But their enemies, the Mutants of Plun-Darr have followed them and it turns out Third Earth already has a Mumm-Ra problem, can Lion-O learn the ropes of being a leader in time?

added.title: The Legend of Boggy Ben
added.description: Lion-O has gotten a hold of the last jar of Thundersnaps, the best cookies Thundera had to offer! But a difficult to open cookie jar is gonna send Lion-O and Cheetara chasing down a legend, a Boggy Ben-related legend.

added.title: Prank Call
added.description: Lion-O wants to prove to the ThunderKittens that he's not just some boring old adult, like Tygra, even if it means ignoring his instincts and messing with an obviously evil crystal.

added.title: The Glitch
added.description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

added.title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
added.description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

added.title: The Maze of the Red Dragon
added.description: Still in the game zone Terra Kerana, the Samurai guide Okino has to choose between helping his allies the ninja, or obeying the evil orders of his Master, Unagami.

added.title: One Step Forward, Two Steps Back
added.description: When the ninja learn that the only way to acquire the second Key-tana is by winning a dangerous race in Terra Technica they'll have to find some racing cars in unexpected ways.

added.title: Racer Seven
added.description: As the ninja prepare for the brutal Speedway Five-Billion race, Lloyd meets a race driver named Seven, who is programmed to lose, but who may hold the key to victory.

added.title: Sand Trap
added.description: Axel and the team take to the desert dunes of a playground sandbox as Madcap attempts to unearth an army of Spy Lizards from the same line as Galileo!

added.title: Dodge City
added.description: Axel embraces the spirit of dodgeball to stop Madcap and Princess SugarSalt's battle over who is the better villain from spilling over into Zoe and Cleo's argument over who is the better coach!

added.title: The Best Team
added.description: When Madcap and his minions crash a soapbox derby, the team must stop the baddies and help Axel - stuck in a car with Luka - cross the finish line!

added.title: Joyride
added.description: At a rummage sale with Uncle Andrew, Axel and Zoe must stop Madcap from turning her long-lost tank toy, Joyride, into an agent of mayhem!

added.title: Savage Axel
added.description: Bearbarian helps Axel get in touch with his wild side as Orangutank "liberates" nature from an apartment building - tossing potted plants of all sizes out the window and onto innocent bystanders below!

added.title: In the Darkness/Indecisive Emily
added.description: An encounter with Storm and his trick rose leaves Magnus temporarily blinded and unable to brawl. With the help of an unlikely partner, Magnus pursues Storm in an attempt to defeat him and restore his vision./ Emily obtains a second Bakugan named Chrissy. It's soon obvious that Emily is having trouble brawling with both Chrissy and Webam, and it's up to Dan, Drago and Gillator to teach them how to brawl as a team.

added.title: The Eclipse/Follow Haavik!
added.description: There's an eclipse happening over Los Volmos, but there's something even more strange going on. Dan and Drago quickly realize something's up; no one seems like themselves today. The two need to get to the bottom of it and return things back to normal./ Magnus and Ajit spot Haavik on the street and decide to follow him, but the shape shifting Haavik is on to them. It's not long before an epic brawl breaks out between them - Five Faction Fusion Sabrus vs. Nillious X Darkus and Pharol.

added.title: Tiko's Back?!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!
added.description: Tiko's Back?!: In order to make Sabrus a 6 faction fusion Bakugan, Haavik heads into the maze to try to capture a golden Bakugan who has brought "mayhem and destruction" to Earth once before - Tiko!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!: The Awesome Brawlers manage to thwart Haavik's attempt to fuse Tiko with Sabrus, but Haavik ends up escaping with the golden Bakugan, Pyravian. Now the Awesome Brawlers must track down Haavik before he can form his ultimate 6 faction fusion Bakugan.

added.title: The AB Bakugan Battle League!
added.description: With all the mayhem and destruction Haavik is causing, the Awesome Brawlers decide that a bit of Bakugan brawling is the perfect distraction to take their minds off all the trouble. With the help of some friends, they start the Awesome Brawler Bakugan Battle league!/ The Awesome Brawler's Bakugan Battle league rages on. Just as the semifinal round comes to a close, an uninvited guest crashes the party, bringing an alarming end to the battle league.

added.title: Haavik's Challenge/Storm Haavik's Tower
added.description: Haavik's Challenge: Haavik has crashed the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan League, and challenges the Awesome Brawlers in a battle league of his own!/ Storm Haavik's Tower: In order to keep Earth and Vestroia safe and rescue Drago, the Awesome Brawlers agree to enter Haavik's Bakugan Battle League, and race toward Haavik's tower for the final showdown.

added.title: El Laberinto del Dragon Rojo
added.description: Aún en la zona de juego de Tierra Karana, Okino tiene que elegir entre ayudar a sus aliados ninjas, u obedecer las órdenes de su Maestro, Unagami.

added.title: Un Paso Adelante, Dos Pasos Atras
added.description: La única manera de que los Ninjas obtengan segunda Keytana es ganando una carrera en Tierra Technica y tiene que conseguir autos de carreras para eso.

added.title: Piloto Siete
added.description: Mientras los Ninjas se preparan para la carrera Cinco Billones por Hora, Lloyd conoce a la Piloto Siete quien puede tener la clave de la victoria.

added.title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
added.description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

added.title: La Falla
added.description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

added.title: #Beeline
added.description: Cuando tropieza con un malvado complot para hacer explotar un puente de la ciudad, Bumblebee se espanta y acude a sus amigas para que derroten a los malhechores. Pero cuando todas sus super amigas están ocupadas, Bumblebee debe buscar cada gramo de coraje en ella para hacer frente a la situación, a pesar de ser la más pequeña del grupo.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #SuperQuien
added.description: Abrumada por la cantidad de cobertura que Superman recibe en las noticias de Metrópolis, Supergirl decide mostrarle a la ciudad lo que puede hacer. Pero cuando Superman pone a todos en peligro sin querer, Supergirl debe decidir si hacer lo que es correcto para la gente o para ella misma.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #CortoCircuito
added.description: Leslie Willis, la chica mas cruel de la escuela, se convierte en una sensación de las redes sociales al subir videos malintencionados a su canal, haciendo que Wonder Woman cuestione la integridad moral de quienes viven en el Mundo del Hombre.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Exodo Parte 2
added.description: En el estreno de dos partes de la serie, León-O y los Thundercats escapan de la destrucción del mundo en el que viven, Thundera, y terminan estrellándose en el misterioso, peligroso y absolutamente increíble Tercer Planeta. Pero sus enemigos, los Mutantes de Plun-Darr, los siguieron. Y resulta que el Tercer Planeta ya tiene un problema llamado Mumm-Ra. ¿Puede León-O aprender las reglas para ser un líder a tiempo?

added.title: Joyride
added.description: iEn una venta de artículos usados ​​con el tío Andrew, Axel y Zoe deben evitar que Madcap convierta su juguete tanque perdido, Joyride, en un agente de caos!

added.title: La Broma
added.description: Cuando intenta demostrarles a los Thundercachorros que no es un adulto aburrido (como Tigro), León-O ignora sus instintos y se mete con un cristal claramente malvado.

added.title: Trampa de Arena
added.description: iAxel y el equipo se dirigen a las dunas del desierto de un cajón de arena en el patio de juegos mientras Madcap intenta desenterrar un ejército de Spy Lizards de la misma línea que Galileo!

added.title: A Esquivar
added.description: iAxel abraza el espíritu del dodgeball para detener la batalla de Madcap y la princesa SugarSalt sobre quién es el mejor villano que se derrama en la discusión de Zoe y Cleo sobre quién es el mejor entrenador!

added.title: La Leyenda de Boggy Ben
added.description: León-O se apoderó del último frasco de Thundersnaps, ilas mejores galletas disponibles en Thundera! Pero un frasco de galletas difícil de abrir hace que León-O y Chitara terminen yendo tras la leyenda de Boggy Ben.

added.title: El Mejor Equipo
added.description: Cuando Madcap y sus secuaces chocan un derby de caja de jabón, el equipo debe detener a los malos y ayudar a Axel, atrapado en un automóvil con Luka, a cruzar la línea de meta.

added.title: El Salvaje Axel
added.description: Bearbarian ayuda a Axel a ponerse en contacto con su lado salvaje mientras Orangutank "libera" la naturaleza de un edificio de apartamentos, arrojando plantas en macetas de todos los tamaños por la ventana y hacia personas inocentes que se encuentran debajo.

added.title: Exodo Parte 1
added.description: En el estreno de dos partes de la serie, León-O y los Thundercats escapan de la destrucción del mundo en el que viven, Thundera, y terminan estrellándose en el misterioso, peligroso y absolutamente increíble Tercer Planeta. Pero sus enemigos, los Mutantes de Plun-Darr, los siguieron. Y resulta que el Tercer Planeta ya tiene un problema llamado Mumm-Ra. ¿Puede León-O aprender las reglas para ser un líder a tiempo?
